 to foster student career success and employability in the global workplace.     Our Values   Education: Prepare students through professional development to build a bridge between college and career.  Diversity: Foster awareness and inclusion of all individuals and their unique contributions to the global workplace.  Service: Provide exemplary customer service that creates a welcoming environment, communicates effectively, and encourages full use of our resources.  Connectedness: Develop relationships with students, employers, and campus partners to support and enhance student success.  Support: Offer comprehensive advising and administrative services to students, employers, and the campus community to facilitate the full-cycle employment process.  Leadership: Guide and empower students to take risks, achieve professional goals, and create a positive impact.          Our Employer Partners   A special thank you to our Academic Year 2020 Employer Partners .  These employers have partnered with UIC Career Services to support student career development.   Central Intelligence Agency  Ulta Beauty Inc.             About    Back to main content           Hours & Location    Our Services    Contact Us    Staff Directory     Career Peer Mentors      Other Career Centers    Newsletters & Recorded Webinars    Frequently Asked Questions                  UIC Logo        Career Services         Students    Career Planning Guide    Make an Appointment    FAQs      Employers    Post a Position    UICcareers.com      Campus Partners    Campus Partners    Program/Workshop Request Forms        Footer Menu    Career Programs and Events    UICcareers    UIC Student Employment Office         Contact   Suite 3050 1200 West Harrison Chicago, IL 60607  Phone: (312) 996-2300  Fax: (312) 413-0383  careerservices@uic.edu        Social Media Accounts    Facebook    Twitter    YouTube             UIC.edu links   UIC.edu  Academic Calendar  Athletics  Campus Directory  Disability Resources  Emer